description: Defines the information that's necessary to populate an ID mapping table.

parameters.name: idMappingTableIdentifier
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the ID mapping table that you want to populate.

parameters.name: membershipIdentifier
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the membership that contains the ID mapping table that you want to populate.

nested_items.name: idMappingJobId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the mapping job that will populate the ID mapping table.
